                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <gloss type="from">United States Vice-Consul-General</gloss> to <persName
                            type="to">M. Bagdasarian</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="hijri gregorian" when="1898-04-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">22d Zeekadeh, 1315</hi> (<hi rend="italic">April 14,
                                1898</hi>)</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 4.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>The foreign minister has telegraphed to the Emir-i-Nizam to order your release.
                    Let me know if it is done.</p>
            </div>
